my C.E.O. Harvey Mason Jr. is doing with the Grammys, which will go on not-=
as-planned on February 2. I imagine the SAG Awards on Netflix will now rais=
e money for its foundation to help displaced SAG-AFTRA members. Critics=E2=
=80=99 Choice Awards? Talent reps should refuse to provide their clients to=
