ward</strong>, ANORA is a film that =E2=80=9D<strong>reaffirms
that movies are still capable of generating miracles</strong>.&#34; (Rollin=
g Stone)</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"><strong><br/></strong>Anchored by an ele=
ctrifying Mikey Madison who delivers<strong> &#34;the performance of the ye=
ar&#34;</strong> (Awards Radar), <strong>ANORA is a timeless and unforgetta=
ble cinematic experience</strong>.</p></div>
